$ /var/db/repos/gentoo/profiles

`/var/db/repos/gentoo/profiles` contains → Linux/distributions/Gentoo#portage-profile[profiles] that are controlled by the developers of the Gentoo → Linux/distributions/Gentoo[ebuild repository] (gentoo.git).

One of them needs to be selected as the system profile. To override these settings, use the files in the `/etc/portage/profile/` directory.

? A subdirectory of this directory is symlinked by `→ Linux/fhs/etc/portage[/etc/portage]/make.profile`

links:
  → https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki//var/db/repos/gentoo/profiles
